---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume · Hanif Carroll" description="Full-stack Product Engineer for early-stage teams.">
  <div class="container space-y-10 py-12">
    <header class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Resume</h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">Full-stack Product Engineer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-primary-foreground transition hover:brightness-110"
          href="/Hanif_Carroll_Product_Engineer.pdf"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Download PDF
        </a>
        <a
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-primary px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-primary transition hover:bg-primary/10"
          href="mailto:HanifCarroll@gmail.com"
        >
          Email Me
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Summary</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
        Product‑minded full‑stack engineer with experience across discovery, UX, and delivery. I’ve shipped 0→1 products as a freelance engineer and led small teams as a fractional CTO. Previously built scheduling and reporting systems at LeagueApps and Nearsure, and shipped enterprise apps at Capgemini. Comfortable owning scope, making pragmatic technical decisions, and delivering fast iterations for early‑stage teams.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">Technical</h3>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li>React, TypeScript, JavaScript, Next.js</li>
          <li>Node.js, HTML, CSS, Tailwind</li>
          <li>Docker, Git</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">Product</h3>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li>User Research, Product Strategy</li>
          <li>Prototyping, Problem Validation</li>
          <li>MVP Development, Agile</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-5">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Experience</h2>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Full‑stack Software Engineer · Freelance · Sep 2024 – Current</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li>Fractional CTO for an emerging social events platform; led a team of 2 juniors.</li>
          <li>Delivered a responsive portfolio site for a comic book artist with a custom interface.</li>
          <li>Built a responsive online catalogue for an auto salvage yard (Webflow).</li>
          <li>Developed targeted landing pages for Light Bearers; produced UX insights via GA/Hotjar.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Senior Front End Engineer · Nearsure · Feb 2023 – Feb 2024</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li>Improved efficiency and UX for 3,000+ sports organizers with an interactive scheduling tool.</li>
          <li>Enhanced mobile editing via an optimized list view for quick event updates.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Front End Engineer · LeagueApps · Nov 2021 – Feb 2023</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li>Reduced scheduling time by 45% with a drag‑and‑drop scheduling grid.</li>
          <li>Built reporting modules with AG Grid; standardized components with Styled Components and Storybook.</li>
          <li>Eliminated double‑booking via automated conflict detection with clear user notifications.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Software Developer · Capgemini · Jan 2019 – Oct 2021</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
          <li>Built a full application for cruise ship and crew management (berthing, reporting, scheduling).</li>
          <li>Led agile development of schedule reporting with designers and analysts.</li>
          <li>Reduced test suite runtime by ~60% and delivered KPI dashboards for leadership.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Featured Projects</h2>
      <ul class="grid gap-2 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
        <li><strong>Vox Prismatic:</strong> Full‑stack SaaS that turns client call transcripts into scheduled LinkedIn posts.</li>
        <li><strong>HablaBA:</strong> local language exchange platform for Buenos Aires, delivered end-to-end from discovery through usability testing.</li>
        <li><strong>Joplin Product Strategy Analysis:</strong> AI‑assisted analysis of 750+ feedback entries to inform roadmap.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
